Build a button for the Excel action.

If the parameter was null this will use the text set up in @TPresenter{decorator= @TDecorator{excelButtonText=''}} but if the given TModelView was not annotated with TPresenter or with a custom view annotation which contains a TPresenter a default string (TAnnotationDefaultValue.TVIEW_excelButtonText) will be used.
